name: Manowixie #004 - LunaPix
description: Diabolus. Fact find pt4: It is just as we feared. The Manowixies are not all good and here is our first encounter of the soul devouring type. They do not stop until they have fully absorbed a soul in its entirety, leaving the victim “empty”. They are not picky and will happily take any soul at all. This particular Manowixie will even eat the souls of its own kind…
